snippet.title: Magocracy: Experimentation Trailer #03
snippet.description:
A trailer for my new game Magocracy: Experimentation. This shows off a 9v9 with the player using a charge shot in an urban environment.

Please visit my website: https://magocracyexperimentation.com/ for more details.
